American Pilot Forced Into Cartel | Aviator | Action Thriller Movie

To help his sick son, an American pilot stranded abroad has no choice but to work with the Colombian drug cartel to escape. But how far is he willing to go to protect those he loves?

2016 Action Thriller Movie | Stars: Ace Marrero, Estefania Borge, Salvatore Basile
